	   <tr><td colspan=2>"I'm wondering what stuff should I be able to get at me level soloing to improve equipment list."<br><br>Your not going to get rich by soloing. SO STOP IT! After you gain a few more levels you will be able to hunt treants in south karana and druids/treants in east karana for TONS of money. Also, if you are low on money go to wisp isle in erud's crossing and kill every wisp you see. Then turn in the greater lightstones at the gypsy camp in north karana to get the concordanance of research book. After you get the book, sell it back to the gypsy lady for 9pp. This works best from levels 8-16, becuase during those levels you will still be getting exp. for the wisps. I supose you could still do it at your level though.<br><br>Former Addict of Everquest<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
