	   <tr><td colspan=2>For the method you are using Earth and Water are the best choices. Earth because it's root makes medding safer, Water because it has better regen and it's spell does damage. Fire and Air just don't have the HPs at this level for this sort of soloing.<br><br>The only GOOD source of money at your level is wisp hunting, but you need to travel for that (Commons is closest point). You will need to summon a dagger(or other weapon) for your pets in order for them to hit the wisps - they don't get to hit magic creatures on their own until the level 12 pet spell, but with a magic weapon they can.<br><br>Level 8 spells you didn't list but need : <br>Shield of Fire (5 or so point Damage shield - mobs will die that much faster)<br>Invisibility (safer travel...)<br>Staff of Tracing (Give one of these to your pet and it will hit for a max of 14, which only your max summon can do on its own. Plus the pet will be able to hit magic-only creatures with it).<br>Dimensional Pocket (optional - 4 slot No-Rent  100% weight reducing bag. lets you collect heavy, low value items that others would just destroy. Usefull if you are scrounging for every last coin..)<br>&nbsp;<br>Zyphyr Runnersbane<br>58th Vending Machine<br>Cult of the Ancient Wyrm<br>Solosek Ro<br></td></tr>
