<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=98451059929207></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f98451059929207><tr><td id=headerrow><span id=sj><a href=/strategy/classes.html?class=12&mid=98451059929207>RE: Hey, I just have some questions</a></span></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?id=18695><span id= >Loeb</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>5 posts</td></tr>
