	   <tr><td colspan=2>Solo'd lvl 50 in 6 hours with one pet.  As long as you know what you are doing, and how to optimize, you can do extremely well.  <br><br>Couple of tricks....<br>1) Learn how to do just a tad bit more then half dmg to the mob. <br><br>2) Solo Low, Low, Low blue<br><br>3) Focus on Mana spent to EP ratio<br><br>4) Use your pet to solo extremely low blues when your pet is healthy and you are low mana, if there is an easy stream of mobs.<br><br>5) JBoots<br><br>6) Fireshield, FS is neutral dmg, and as such you can lower the amount of dmg you have to do to beat your pet.<br><br>7) know how much dmg you need to do to beat your pet, burn that much then med for the rest of the combat.<br><br>--tensor<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
