	   <tr><td colspan=2>All of the level 20 pets can be found in OOT. There is a female vendor in a small tower on the island next to sister island who sells them. As for spell components... the hermit, treants, aviaks, and gnolls, ALL found in south karana, drop level 20 and 24 reseraching materials.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
