	   <tr><td colspan=2>Kadthar here,<br><br>I'm based on the other side of Antonica (near Qeynos) so it was a while before I got my level 16 and 20 pets other than the ones that are generally available at the guild.  I did manage to cross the continent and ride the boat out to the Ocean of Tears to buy all the spells when I was level 17 (almost 18 by that time).  If you start on Faydwer or in Neriak or Freeport there should be little difficulty other than the wait for the boat.  I'm going to post an in-depth description of how I went through it as a separate post....I was very careful and was never in danger of dying as a result.<br><br>Kadthar<br>Level 18 Erudite Gatecaller (Magician)<br>&lt;Divinity&gt;<br>Tholuxe Paells<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
