	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have 1 correction you stated that a mage can't solo in Kedge Keep. The best exp I found for lvl's 36 to about 40 was at the zone in to kedge. Just the first room You will find plenty of Lancers to pull. Just use your lvl 1 spell to pull them to zone. With the fire pet you can clean up in here. Just summon a lot of waterstones and if you need to go afk for even a couple seconds use one before afk. Your stamina will bottom out but not a big deal. Your swimming will max fast. And as stated not many people come here except for raids on Phinny who btw drops the Staff of Elemental Mastery Water.  So not apt to see 1 train. Only thing that got me was when a group came in to do a raid they would clean house on the first room before moving on. Which they need to do but stops your exp for a few mins. But well worth it.<br><br>Cilditin 52nd Elementalst on Povar<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
