	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ummm....if you go invis your pet dies. To kill the paladin use an earth pet and kite him around with it. To outrun a player that doesn't have sow, hold the ctrl. key and one of the directional keys while running. The effect is that you will strafe while running, let you outrun other players. While running around your earth pet will be beating on him and eventually root him. Once he is rooted stop running and blast him. He will be able to get a lay hands off, but as long as you keep enough mana stored up for a second pet, just in case your first one dies, you will be able to kite him around and eventually win.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
